description: Don't miss the opportunity! This magnificent sunny penthouse unit has direct elevator access. It's a prime location near the Seaport and South End, with a very high walking score, as it's minutes away from the grocery, top restaurants, and the T. In addition, all major highways are nearby and easily accessible. This light-filled residence spans 1135 sq/  features 2 full bedrooms and bathrooms. Both bedrooms feature custom walk-in closets. The ensuite bathroom is styled with glass tile and a frameless shower door. The two-tone paneled kitchen offers high-end appliances, decorative lighting, oversized quartz countertops, a pot filler, and a farmhouse sink. The shiplap accent wall, wide plank, white oak floors, and gas fireplace with built-in stone insert speakers add to the high-style wireless temperature control, and a Naviance on-demand water heater help with the condo's energy usage. The unit has deeded roof rights with architecture plans, as well as deeded parking in the garage.
